    <entry>
      <title>LAMP&amp;LNMP搭建网站</title>
      <link href="/posts/37b01ca4.html"/>
      <url>/posts/37b01ca4.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>LAMP 和 LNMP 是 Linux 服务器上最常见的两种 Web 服务架构：</p><table><thead><tr><th>架构</th><th>组件</th><th>区别</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>LAMP</strong></td><td>Linux + Apache + MySQL + PHP</td><td>Apache 处理 PHP 通过模块嵌入</td></tr><tr><td><strong>LNMP</strong></td><td>Linux + Nginx + MySQL + PHP</td><td>Nginx 通过 FastCGI 转发 PHP 请求给 php-fpm</td></tr></tbody></table><p>本文演示如何用这两种架构分别搭建网站。</p><hr><h2 id="一、LAMP-搭建-Discuz-论坛"><a href="#一、LAMP-搭建-Discuz-论坛" class="headerlink" title="一、LAMP 搭建 Discuz 论坛"></a>一、LAMP 搭建 Discuz 论坛</h2><h3 id="环境说明"><a href="#环境说明" class="headerlink" title="环境说明"></a>环境说明</h3><ul><li>系统：CentOS 7</li><li>IP：192.168.19.130</li></ul><h3 id="1-1-安装-Apache"><a href="#1-1-安装-Apache" class="headerlink" title="1.1 安装 Apache"></a>1.1 安装 Apache</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install httpd -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-安装-PHP"><a href="#1-2-安装-PHP" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装 PHP"></a>1.2 安装 PHP</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install php -y</span><br><span class="line">yum install php php-* -y --skip-broken</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-配置-Apache-解析-PHP"><a href="#1-3-配置-Apache-解析-PHP" class="headerlink" title="1.3 配置 Apache 解析 PHP"></a>1.3 配置 Apache 解析 PHP</h3><p>编辑 Apache 配置文件，让服务器支持 PHP：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在文件中添加以下内容（按 <code>o</code> 在下一行插入）：</p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">AddType <span class="built_in">application</span>/x-httpd-php .php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启 Apache：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl restart httpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-4-验证-PHP-环境"><a href="#1-4-验证-PHP-环境" class="headerlink" title="1.4 验证 PHP 环境"></a>1.4 验证 PHP 环境</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /var/www/html</span><br><span class="line">vi index.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入测试代码：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="title function_ invoke__">phpinfo</span>(); <span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器访问 <code>http://192.168.19.130</code>，出现 PHP 信息页说明环境配置成功。</p><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_1_1.jpeg" alt="PHP 环境验证"></p><h3 id="1-5-下载-Discuz-源码"><a href="#1-5-下载-Discuz-源码" class="headerlink" title="1.5 下载 Discuz 源码"></a>1.5 下载 Discuz 源码</h3><p>将 Discuz 源码包下载到服务器，解压并移动到网站目录：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> Discuz_X3.2_SC_UTF8.zip /var/www/html/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /var/www/html/</span><br><span class="line">unzip Discuz_X3.2_SC_UTF8.zip</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 upload/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_1_2.jpeg" alt="下载 Discuz 源码"></p><h3 id="1-6-安装-Discuz"><a href="#1-6-安装-Discuz" class="headerlink" title="1.6 安装 Discuz"></a>1.6 安装 Discuz</h3><p>浏览器访问 <code>http://192.168.19.130/upload</code>，进入 Discuz 安装向导。</p><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_2_1.jpeg" alt="Discuz 安装界面"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_2_2.jpeg" alt="安装向导"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_2_3.jpeg" alt="填写数据库"></p><p>按照页面提示填写数据库信息和管理员账号，点击安装。</p><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_3_1.jpeg" alt="开始安装"></p><h3 id="1-7-安装完成"><a href="#1-7-安装完成" class="headerlink" title="1.7 安装完成"></a>1.7 安装完成</h3><p>安装完成后进入数据库查看，发现多了一个数据库，正是安装过程中创建的。</p><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_3_2.jpeg" alt="安装完成"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_4_1.jpeg" alt="数据库验证"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_4_2.jpeg" alt="LNMP 开始"></p><hr><h2 id="二、LNMP-搭建网站"><a href="#二、LNMP-搭建网站" class="headerlink" title="二、LNMP 搭建网站"></a>二、LNMP 搭建网站</h2><p>LNMP 使用 <strong>Nginx</strong> 替代 Apache，通过 <strong>php-fpm</strong> 处理 PHP，具有更高的并发处理能力。</p><h3 id="2-1-安装数据库-MariaDB"><a href="#2-1-安装数据库-MariaDB" class="headerlink" title="2.1 安装数据库 MariaDB"></a>2.1 安装数据库 MariaDB</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install mariadb -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-2-配置-YUM-源"><a href="#2-2-配置-YUM-源" class="headerlink" title="2.2 配置 YUM 源"></a>2.2 配置 YUM 源</h3><p>先备份原有 YUM 源，再替换为阿里云镜像：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 备份</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.bak</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载阿里云源</span></span><br><span class="line">wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理并重建缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">yum clean all</span><br><span class="line">yum makecache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-3-安装-Nginx"><a href="#2-3-安装-Nginx" class="headerlink" title="2.3 安装 Nginx"></a>2.3 安装 Nginx</h3><p>添加 Nginx 官方 YUM 源：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/yum.repos.d/nginx.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入：</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[nginx]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">name</span>=nginx_repo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">baseurl</span>=http://nginx.org/packages/centos/<span class="number">7</span>/<span class="variable">$basearch</span>/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">gpgcheck</span>=<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">enabled</span>=<span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum list nginx          <span class="comment"># 查询可用版本</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install nginx -y    <span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart nginx <span class="comment"># 启动服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_5_1.jpeg" alt="Nginx 安装"></p><h3 id="2-4-安装-PHP-和-php-fpm"><a href="#2-4-安装-PHP-和-php-fpm" class="headerlink" title="2.4 安装 PHP 和 php-fpm"></a>2.4 安装 PHP 和 php-fpm</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install php -y</span><br><span class="line">yum install php php-* -y --skip-broken</span><br><span class="line">yum install php-fpm -y           <span class="comment"># 安装 FastCGI 进程管理器</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl start php-fpm           <span class="comment"># 启动 php-fpm</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>验证 php-fpm 是否启动（默认监听 9000 端口）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsof -i:9000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-5-配置-Nginx-解析-PHP"><a href="#2-5-配置-Nginx-解析-PHP" class="headerlink" title="2.5 配置 Nginx 解析 PHP"></a>2.5 配置 Nginx 解析 PHP</h3><p>编辑 Nginx 默认配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完整配置如下：</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">server</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">listen</span>       <span class="number">80</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">server_name</span>  localhost;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="section">location</span> / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">root</span>   /usr/share/nginx/html;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">index</span>  index.html index.htm index.php;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">error_page</span>  <span class="number">500</span> <span class="number">502</span> <span class="number">503</span> <span class="number">504</span>  /50x.html;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="section">location</span> = /50x.html &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">root</span>   /usr/share/nginx/html;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 将 PHP 请求转发给 FastCGI</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="section">location</span> <span class="regexp">~ \.php$</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">root</span>           /usr/share/nginx/html;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">fastcgi_pass</span>   <span class="number">127.0.0.1:9000</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">fastcgi_index</span>  index.php;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">fastcgi_param</span>  SCRIPT_FILENAME  <span class="variable">$document_root</span><span class="variable">$fastcgi_script_name</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">include</span>        fastcgi_params;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新载入 Nginx：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl reload nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_6_1.jpeg" alt="Nginx PHP 配置1"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_6_2.jpeg" alt="Nginx PHP 配置2"></p><h3 id="2-6-验证-PHP-解析"><a href="#2-6-验证-PHP-解析" class="headerlink" title="2.6 验证 PHP 解析"></a>2.6 验证 PHP 解析</h3><p>在网站根目录创建 <code>index.php</code>：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="title function_ invoke__">phpinfo</span>(); <span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器访问服务器 IP，看到 PHP 信息页即表示 Nginx + PHP 配置成功。</p><h3 id="2-7-部署网站源码"><a href="#2-7-部署网站源码" class="headerlink" title="2.7 部署网站源码"></a>2.7 部署网站源码</h3><p>将源码包移动到 Nginx 网站目录并解压：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> /root/Discuz_X3.2_SC_UTF8.zip /usr/share/nginx/html</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/share/nginx/html</span><br><span class="line">unzip qqfarm-master.zip</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 qqfarm-master/upload/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_8_1.jpeg" alt="源码部署1"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_8_2.jpeg" alt="源码部署2"></p><h3 id="2-8-创建数据库并导入"><a href="#2-8-创建数据库并导入" class="headerlink" title="2.8 创建数据库并导入"></a>2.8 创建数据库并导入</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p123456</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> DATABASE qqfarm;</span><br><span class="line">EXIT;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>导入 SQL 数据：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p qqfarm &lt; qqfarm.sql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>网站目录为：<code>/usr/share/nginx/html/qqfarm-master/upload</code></p><p><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_9_1.jpeg" alt="数据库操作1"><br><img src="/assets/lamp-lnmp/lamp_img_9_2.jpeg" alt="数据库操作2"></p><hr><h2 id="三、LAMP-vs-LNMP-对比总结"><a href="#三、LAMP-vs-LNMP-对比总结" class="headerlink" title="三、LAMP vs LNMP 对比总结"></a>三、LAMP vs LNMP 对比总结</h2><table><thead><tr><th>对比维度</th><th align="center">LAMP (Apache)</th><th align="center">LNMP (Nginx)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>处理方式</strong></td><td align="center">模块化嵌入 PHP</td><td align="center">FastCGI 转发</td></tr><tr><td><strong>并发性能</strong></td><td align="center">中等</td><td align="center"><strong>高</strong>（异步非阻塞）</td></tr><tr><td><strong>静态文件</strong></td><td align="center">一般</td><td align="center"><strong>极快</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>配置复杂度</strong></td><td align="center">简单</td><td align="center">稍复杂</td></tr><tr><td><strong>.htaccess</strong></td><td align="center">✅ 支持</td><td align="center">❌ 不支持</td></tr><tr><td><strong>适用场景</strong></td><td align="center">小型站点、虚拟主机</td><td align="center">高并发、反向代理</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h2><p>无论是 LAMP 还是 LNMP，核心流程都是：</p><ol><li><strong>搭建 Web 服务器</strong>（Apache &#x2F; Nginx）</li><li><strong>安装 PHP 运行环境</strong>（模块 &#x2F; php-fpm）</li><li><strong>安装数据库</strong>（MySQL &#x2F; MariaDB）</li><li><strong>部署网站源码</strong> → 解压 → 授权 → 配置</li><li><strong>创建数据库并导入数据</strong></li></ol><p>掌握这两种架构的搭建方法，基本能应对大多数 PHP 网站的部署需求。</p>]]></content>
      
      
